reviewText: This was beyond a waste of my money and time.  This was listed as a beginner program...however nothing was explained or spelled out.  The "Instructor" shows the process then expects you to do it without explaining anything.  I have watched free Youtube videos with more value than this course.  I have been using Coursera for a long time and this is by far THE WORST WASTE OF MY TIME YET!!!!There was nothing beginner about this "Course" and nothing was explained!!! You should be ashamed of yourselves charging for this and taking advantage of people looking for quality training.  This certainly is NOT up to the Coursera standards.Avoid this at all costs unless you already know how to use excel and these advanced functions.   It may be a refresher at best!
